<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine Service, Model Year 1994 - 1998 - HIGH PRESSURE OIL PUMP -
        Installation - High Pressure Oil Pump and Drive Gear
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc graphiccount="3">
        <title>High Pressure Oil Pump and Drive Gear</title>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Two different types of pump gaskets are available. Make sure the correct type is being
                    installed.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="f1201111" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figeg3/eg3513.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="yes"/>
            <caption>Installing the Drive Gear and Gasket</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">High Pressure Pump Gasket</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Front Cover</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">High Pressure Pump</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Insert the high pressure oil pump drive gear through the opening on top of the front
                cover.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Position the high pressure oil pump with the gasket against the front cover.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1201112" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figeg3/eg3514.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="yes"/>
            <caption>Installing the High Pressure Oil Pump</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Front Cover</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">High Pressure Oil Pump Mounting Bolts (2)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">High Pressure Oil Pump</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Secure the oil pump to the front cover with two mounting bolts.</para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1201113" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figeg3/eg3263.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="yes"/>
            <caption>Installing the High Pressure Oil Pump Drive Gear</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">High Pressure Oil Pump Drive Gear</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Front Cover</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">High Pressure Oil Pump Drive Gear Mounting Bolt</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Washer</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Secure the drive gear to the high pressure oil pump with the washer and mounting bolt.
                Tighten the bolt to the special torque value.
            </para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
